02:31:43.349 --> 02:31:53.719
It's like I can see it, buddy. I pray over those ground troops.

02:31:53.720 --> 02:31:59.567
I pray over people. I pray over them. Father, I pray over them.

02:31:59.568 --> 02:32:05.559
Father, that the angels of the Lord are kept around our men and women of service, our Navy Seals.

02:32:05.560 --> 02:32:16.638
I pray over them. I pray a hedge around and about them in Jesus'name. I pray over Israel's secret people.

02:32:16.639 --> 02:32:29.279
I pray a hedge around and about them in Jesus'name, over Israel's skies, over their Iron Dome, over the Golden Dome, over all of it.

02:32:29.280 --> 02:32:42.670
Father, we pray a hedge of protection round and about them in Jesus'mighty name. We pray over our Coast Guard around Miami.

02:32:42.671 --> 02:33:05.665
We pray over our Coast Guard that they see anybody moving in the night and that everything is brought to light in Jesus'name.

02:33:05.666 --> 02:34:06.885
The river of that is so intense. Do you feel it? I feel it. It pulls so hard tonight as I lift my hands to you, Lord.

02:34:06.886 --> 02:37:33.399
Father, we worship you for a great nation. Holy Spirit, come. We give you all the glory, the honor, and the praise.

02:37:33.400 --> 02:37:46.631
I pray over those boats, over our aircraft carriers, and over biological weapons.

02:37:46.632 --> 02:38:45.839
I pray that every biological payload falls into the ocean. Over our boats and over our bases, you protect every single one of them.

02:38:45.840 --> 02:38:58.799
Father, angels of the Lord are camping around about them. No weapon formed against them will prosper.

02:38:58.800 --> 02:39:46.999
Father, we worship you. This is an arrogant display. I will let you all go.

02:39:47.000 --> 02:39:57.359
I will keep praying. Keep praying. The pulse is very intense.

02:39:57.360 --> 02:40:06.178
Remember I told you there are certain pulses that we pray, and when we hit those pulses, we can feel it go; it is a very intense pulse.

02:40:06.179 --> 02:40:17.359
This is one that is so intense right now. I feel like I am having you search the news as I am telling you. I feel it is about to happen.

02:40:17.360 --> 02:40:27.999
It is very intense, and it concerns these drones with biological payloads regarding our men and women of service.

02:40:28.000 --> 02:40:36.959
It is some kind of yellowed liquid to spray and gas to try to hurt our people, our bases, and our areas.

02:40:36.960 --> 02:40:52.879
It is biological, chemical warfare. We love every single one of you.

02:40:52.880 --> 02:40:58.919
Thank you for coming out tonight. We are so grateful for every one of you every time.

02:40:58.920 --> 02:41:09.319
There are 7,100 of you right now, and we are so grateful that you would pray with us and spend your night praying over it with us.

02:41:09.320 --> 02:41:31.934
It is such an honor. China is close to allowing Iran to buy supersonic anti-ship missiles.

02:41:31.935 --> 02:41:38.623
Reports. This is what I am talking about. It is secret things that they do not know.

02:41:38.624 --> 02:41:54.199
I told you they are bringing them on. They see these big airplanes in the middle of the night.

02:41:54.200 --> 02:42:07.239
It was a surprise. When I was in the spirit, I saw the surprise like Pearl Harbor.

02:42:07.240 --> 02:42:21.679
That was such an intense pull. Do not underestimate your enemy.

02:42:21.680 --> 02:42:25.759
Never look at the top, thinking you are the big guy on campus.

02:42:25.760 --> 02:42:39.992
You need to realize that the nerdy guy at the table is the one who has the secret power.

02:42:39.993 --> 02:42:51.722
You do not know it. It is not funny. It is very serious. We love you all. We will close it there.

02:42:51.723 --> 02:42:56.079
We could pray into this all night long, but sometimes you just unhook.

02:42:56.080 --> 02:43:03.639
I will keep praying as I was before. Keep praying over our boats.

02:43:03.640 --> 02:43:07.874
It is very serious about our boats tonight. Pray over your boats.

02:43:07.875 --> 02:43:19.159
Pray over our air bases. We love you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:43:19.160 --> 02:43:26.260
Remember, we love you and Jesus loves you. We will see you again.

